<div id="main_content">
	<h2>$2 Million Gift Starts UCFs Drive for New National Reading Center</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Chad Binette
		
		<span class="date">April 1, 2005</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/0/NE465/en_US/reading1main.jpg" height="" width=""  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jacque Brund</p>
			
			<p>John Morgridge signs a check for a $2 million donation he and his wife, Carrie, left, gave to create a new reading center at the UCF College of Education.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=002400413206c3010220adacf2006fcf">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
								<h3>Story Images</h3>
								<ul id="story_images">
							
						<li>
						<a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=002400413206c3010220adacf2006fcf&amp;img_mode=1&amp;index=0">
							<img width="100" alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/0/NE465/en_US/reading3.jpg"  />
						</a>
						</li>
						
						
					
			
					
						
						
							
						<li>
						<a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=002400413206c3010220adacf2006fcf&amp;img_mode=1&amp;index=1">
							<img width="100" alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/0/NE465/en_US/reading2full.jpg"  />
						</a>
						</li>
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			</ul><p  class="note">Click thumbnails for full-size images.</p>
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
			<div id="related">
